    question: '<p>Which form attribute is used to allow the user the option to enter more than one value in an input element, such as input and file?</p>\n<pre><code class="language-html">&#x3C;form action="file.php">\n Select images:\n  &#x3C;input type="file"\n    name="img" ???>\n &#x3C;input type="submit">\n&#x3C;/form>\n</code></pre>\n',
